<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Women's Revolt™ — I Personaggi</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    :root {
      --red: #9B0000;
      --red-light: #C0392B;
      --gold: #B8960C;
      --off-white: #F5F0E8;
      --dark: #0A0A0A;
      --card-bg: #0F0F0F;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--off-white);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 24px 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.97) 0%, transparent 100%);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--off-white);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--red-light); }
    .lang-switcher { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .lang-btn {
      background: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .lang-btn:hover { border-color: var(--red-light); color: var(--red-light); }
    .lang-btn.active { background: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); color: #fff; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 160px 48px 80px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 30% 0%, rgba(155,0,0,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red-light);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: block;
    }
    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 88px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }
    .hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.4); }
    .hero-desc {
      margin-top: 32px;
      max-width: 500px;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 2;
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.5);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }
    .divider-line { width: 48px; height: 1px; background: var(--red); margin: 36px 0; }

    /* ── NURSES SECTION ── */
    .section-title {
      padding: 0 48px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .section-title h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    }
    .section-title .red-line {
      width: 32px; height: 1px;
      background: var(--red);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    /* ── GRID NURSES (2x2) ── */
    .nurses-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
      padding: 0 0 2px;
    }

    /* ── GRID ALLIES (2 wide) ── */
    .allies-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    /* ── CHARACTER CARD ── */
    .char-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      padding: 52px 48px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: background 0.4s;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .char-card:hover { background: #141414; }

    /* Accent line top */
    .char-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--red);
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.77,0,0.175,1);
    }
    .char-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

    /* Big initial letter */
    .char-initial {
      position: absolute;
      right: 32px; bottom: -20px;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 160px;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      line-height: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: color 0.4s;
    }
    .char-card:hover .char-initial { color: rgba(155,0,0,0.07); }

    .char-role {
      font-size: 9px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--red-light);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .char-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 46px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .char-origin {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .char-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(245,240,232,0.58);
      max-width: 380px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .char-desc strong { color: var(--off-white); font-weight: 400; }

    .char-tags {
      margin-top: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .char-tag {
      font-size: 8px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 4px 10px;
    }

    .char-casting {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(184,150,12,0.6);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    .char-casting span { color: rgba(184,150,12,0.9); font-style: italic; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; text-transform: none; }

    /* ── BOTTOM BAR ── */
    .bottom-bar {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      padding: 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .trademark { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); letter-spacing: 3px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 32px; }
    .nav-link {
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 4px; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .nav-link:hover { color: var(--red-light); }
    .nav-link.active-page { color: var(--red-light); }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .char-card { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both; }
    .char-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
    .char-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
    .char-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
    .char-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.35s; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 20px 24px; }
      .hero { padding: 130px 24px 60px; }
      .section-title { padding: 0 24px; }
      .nurses-grid, .allies-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .char-card { padding: 40px 24px; }
      .char-initial { font-size: 110px; }
      .bottom-bar { padding: 32px 24px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }

    /* ── LANG ── */
    [data-lang] { display: none; }
    [data-lang].active { display: block; }
    [data-lang-inline] { display: none; }
    [data-lang-inline].active { display: inline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a class="nav-logo" href="index.html">Women's Revolt<span>™</span></a>
  <div class="lang-switcher">
    <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('it')">IT</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('fr')">FR</button>
    <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('es')">ES</button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <span class="section-label">Women's Revolt™</span>
  <h1 class="hero-title">
    <span data-lang="it" class="active">Le<br><em>Donne</em></span>
    <span data-lang="en">The<br><em>Women</em></span>
    <span data-lang="fr">Les<br><em>Femmes</em></span>
    <span data-lang="es">Las<br><em>Mujeres</em></span>
  </h1>
  <div class="divider-line"></div>
  <p class="hero-desc">
    <span data-lang="it" class="active">Sei donne. Una rivolta. Nessuna di loro ha scelto di diventare un simbolo — è successo perché non avevano altra scelta.</span>
    <span data-lang="en">Six women. One revolt. None of them chose to become a symbol — it happened because they had no other choice.</span>
    <span data-lang="fr">Six femmes. Une révolte. Aucune d'elles n'a choisi de devenir un symbole — c'est arrivé parce qu'elles n'avaient pas d'autre choix.</span>
    <span data-lang="es">Seis mujeres. Una revuelta. Ninguna eligió convertirse en símbolo — ocurrió porque no tenían otra opción.</span>
  </p>
</section>

<!-- NURSES LABEL -->
<div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 40px;">
  <h2>
    <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Le Quattro Infermiere</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="en">The Four Nurses</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="fr">Les Quatre Infirmières</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="es">Las Cuatro Enfermeras</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="red-line"></div>
</div>

<!-- NURSES GRID -->
<div class="nurses-grid">

  <!-- BRENDA -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">B</div>
    <div class="char-role">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Infermiera · Protagonista</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Nurse · Protagonist</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Infirmière · Protagoniste</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Enfermera · Protagonista</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="char-name">Brenda</h2>
    <div class="char-origin">American</div>
    <p class="char-desc">
      <span data-lang="it" class="active">La più determinata del gruppo. Brenda non alza mai la voce — non ne ha bisogno. Sa esattamente dove vuole arrivare e non si ferma davanti a niente. È lei che tiene insieme le altre quando tutto rischia di crollare. Sua figlia <strong>Mia</strong>. Suo marito <strong>Tom Cole</strong> — condannato a <strong>5 anni</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">The most determined of the group. Brenda never raises her voice — she doesn't need to. She knows exactly where she's going and nothing stops her. She's the one who holds the others together when everything is about to fall apart. Her daughter <strong>Mia</strong>. Her husband <strong>Tom Cole</strong> — sentenced to <strong>5 years</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="fr">La plus déterminée du groupe. Brenda n'élève jamais la voix — elle n'en a pas besoin. Elle sait exactement où elle va et rien ne l'arrête. C'est elle qui maintient les autres ensemble quand tout risque de s'effondrer. Sa fille <strong>Mia</strong>. Son mari <strong>Tom Cole</strong> — condamné à <strong>5 ans</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="es">La más decidida del grupo. Brenda nunca levanta la voz — no lo necesita. Sabe exactamente adónde quiere llegar y nada la detiene. Es ella quien mantiene unidas a las demás cuando todo está a punto de derrumbarse. Su hija <strong>Mia</strong>. Su marido <strong>Tom Cole</strong> — condenado a <strong>5 años</strong>.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="char-casting">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">La produzione è alla ricerca del miglior cast internazionale</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Production is seeking the finest international cast</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">La production recherche les meilleurs acteurs internationaux</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">La producción buscará el mejor elenco internacional</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- JENNY -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">J</div>
    <div class="char-role">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Infermiera · Protagonista</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Nurse · Protagonist</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Infirmière · Protagoniste</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Enfermera · Protagonista</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="char-name">Jenny</h2>
    <div class="char-origin">Latin American</div>
    <p class="char-desc">
      <span data-lang="it" class="active">La più emotiva — e la più coraggiosa. Jenny sente tutto più degli altri e lo dice. Non mente, non nasconde, non trattiene. È questa trasparenza che la rende pericolosa agli occhi del sistema. Sua figlia <strong>Sofia</strong>. Suo marito <strong>Bryan Harris</strong> — condannato a <strong>3 anni</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">The most emotional — and the most courageous. Jenny feels everything more than the others and she says it. She doesn't lie, doesn't hide, doesn't hold back. It's this transparency that makes her dangerous in the system's eyes. Her daughter <strong>Sofia</strong>. Her husband <strong>Bryan Harris</strong> — sentenced to <strong>3 years</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="fr">La plus émotive — et la plus courageuse. Jenny ressent tout plus que les autres et le dit. Elle ne ment pas, ne cache rien, ne se retient pas. C'est cette transparence qui la rend dangereuse aux yeux du système. Sa fille <strong>Sofia</strong>. Son mari <strong>Bryan Harris</strong> — condamné à <strong>3 ans</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="es">La más emocional — y la más valiente. Jenny siente todo más que las demás y lo dice. No miente, no esconde, no se contiene. Es esta transparencia la que la hace peligrosa a los ojos del sistema. Su hija <strong>Sofia</strong>. Su marido <strong>Bryan Harris</strong> — condenado a <strong>3 años</strong>.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="char-casting">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">La produzione è alla ricerca del miglior cast internazionale</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Production is seeking the finest international cast</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">La production recherche les meilleurs acteurs internationaux</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">La producción buscará el mejor elenco internacional</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LINDSAY -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">L</div>
    <div class="char-role">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Infermiera · Protagonista</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Nurse · Protagonist</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Infirmière · Protagoniste</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Enfermera · Protagonista</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="char-name">Lindsay</h2>
    <div class="char-origin">Korean American</div>
    <p class="char-desc">
      <span data-lang="it" class="active">La strategica. Lindsay non agisce mai senza aver pensato tre mosse avanti. Analizza, aspetta, colpisce nel momento giusto. La sua forza è la precisione — e il suo silenzio è più eloquente di qualsiasi discorso. Sua figlia <strong>Emily</strong>. Suo marito <strong>Peter Park</strong> — condannato a <strong>4 anni</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">The strategist. Lindsay never acts without thinking three moves ahead. She analyzes, waits, strikes at the right moment. Her strength is precision — and her silence is more eloquent than any speech. Her daughter <strong>Emily</strong>. Her husband <strong>Peter Park</strong> — sentenced to <strong>4 years</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="fr">La stratège. Lindsay n'agit jamais sans avoir réfléchi trois coups à l'avance. Elle analyse, attend, frappe au bon moment. Sa force est la précision — et son silence est plus éloquent que n'importe quel discours. Sa fille <strong>Emily</strong>. Son mari <strong>Peter Park</strong> — condamné à <strong>4 ans</strong>.</span>
      <span data-lang="es">La estratega. Lindsay nunca actúa sin haber pensado tres movimientos por adelantado. Analiza, espera, golpea en el momento justo. Su fuerza es la precisión — y su silencio es más elocuente que cualquier discurso. Su hija <strong>Emily</strong>. Su marido <strong>Peter Park</strong> — condenado a <strong>4 años</strong>.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="char-casting">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">La produzione è alla ricerca del miglior cast internazionale</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Production is seeking the finest international cast</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">La production recherche les meilleurs acteurs internationaux</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">La producción buscará el mejor elenco internacional</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SHANE -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">S</div>
    <div class="char-role">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Infermiera · Protagonista</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Nurse · Protagonist</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Infirmière · Protagoniste</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Enfermera · Protagonista</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="char-name">Shane</h2>
    <div class="char-origin">African American</div>
    <p class="char-desc">
      <span data-lang="it" class="active">La voce morale del gruppo. Shane porta dentro di sé una storia più lunga di questa rivolta — e lo sa. Ogni sua parola pesa perché viene da un posto reale, non da una teoria. È lei che ricorda alle altre cosa c'è davvero in gioco. Sua figlia <strong>Layla</strong>. Suo marito <strong>James Washington</strong> — servizio alla comunità.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">The moral voice of the group. Shane carries within her a history longer than this revolt — and she knows it. Every word she says carries weight because it comes from a real place, not a theory. She's the one who reminds the others what is truly at stake. Her daughter <strong>Layla</strong>. Her husband <strong>James Washington</strong> — community service.</span>
      <span data-lang="fr">La voix morale du groupe. Shane porte en elle une histoire plus longue que cette révolte — et elle le sait. Chaque mot qu'elle dit a du poids parce qu'il vient d'un endroit réel, pas d'une théorie. C'est elle qui rappelle aux autres ce qui est vraiment en jeu. Sa fille <strong>Layla</strong>. Son mari <strong>James Washington</strong> — service communautaire.</span>
      <span data-lang="es">La voz moral del grupo. Shane lleva dentro una historia más larga que esta revuelta — y lo sabe. Cada palabra suya tiene peso porque viene de un lugar real, no de una teoría. Es ella quien recuerda a las demás lo que está verdaderamente en juego. Su hija <strong>Layla</strong>. Su marido <strong>James Washington</strong> — servicio comunitario.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="char-casting">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">La produzione è alla ricerca del miglior cast internazionale</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Production is seeking the finest international cast</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">La production recherche les meilleurs acteurs internationaux</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">La producción buscará el mejor elenco internacional</span>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- ALLIES LABEL -->
<div class="section-title" style="margin-top: 40px;">
  <h2>
    <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Le Alleate</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="en">The Allies</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="fr">Les Alliées</span>
    <span data-lang-inline="es">Las Aliadas</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="red-line"></div>
</div>

<!-- ALLIES GRID -->
<div class="allies-grid">

  <!-- JANET MOODY -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">J</div>
    <div class="char-role">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Giudice · Alleata</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Judge · Ally</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Juge · Alliée</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Jueza · Aliada</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="char-name">Janet Moody</h2>
    <div class="char-origin">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">Magistratura</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Judiciary</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">Magistrature</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">Magistratura</span>
    </div>
    <p class="char-desc">
      <span data-lang="it" class="active">Non è una rivoluzionaria. Non si è mai definita tale. Janet Moody è qualcosa di più difficile da sconfiggere: è una donna che conosce la legge meglio di chiunque altro — e ha deciso di usarla nel modo in cui avrebbe sempre dovuto essere usata. Il suo tribunale diventa il primo fronte della rivolta.</span>
      <span data-lang="en">She is not a revolutionary. She has never called herself one. Janet Moody is something harder to defeat: a woman who knows the law better than anyone — and has decided to use it the way it should always have been used. Her courtroom becomes the first front of the revolt.</span>
      <span data-lang="fr">Elle n'est pas une révolutionnaire. Elle ne s'est jamais appelée ainsi. Janet Moody est quelque chose de plus difficile à vaincre : une femme qui connaît la loi mieux que quiconque — et qui a décidé de l'utiliser comme elle aurait toujours dû l'être. Son tribunal devient le premier front de la révolte.</span>
      <span data-lang="es">No es una revolucionaria. Nunca se ha definido como tal. Janet Moody es algo más difícil de vencer: una mujer que conoce la ley mejor que nadie — y ha decidido usarla como siempre debió usarse. Su tribunal se convierte en el primer frente de la revuelta.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="char-casting">
      <span data-lang-inline="it" class="active">La produzione è alla ricerca del miglior cast internazionale</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="en">Production is seeking the finest international cast</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="fr">La production recherche les meilleurs acteurs internationaux</span>
      <span data-lang-inline="es">La producción buscará el mejor elenco internacional</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BETTY LANGSTON -->
  <div class="char-card">
    <div class="char-initial">B</div>
    <div class="char-role">
